3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-to-boycott-tv-shows-that-conduct-inflammatory-debates%5C%22%3EIndia%20Alliance%20to%20Boycott%20TV%20Shows%20That%20%E2%80%98Conduct%20Inflammatory%20Debates%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Saturday%2C%20September%2016%2C%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%20that%20the%20move%20to%20not%20participate%20in%20these%20shows%20was%20not%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cboycott%E2%80%9D%20but%20instead%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnon-cooperation%20movement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20banned%2C%20boycotted%20or%20blacklisted%20anyone.%20This%20is%20a%20non-cooperation%20movement%2C%20we%20will%20not%20cooperate%20with%20anyone%20spreading%20hatred%20in%20the%20society.%20We%20are%20not%20stopping%20them%20from%20spreading%20hatred.%20You%20want%20to%20spread%20hatred%2C%20go%20ahead%20and%20do%20it.%20You%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20do%20it.%20We%20also%20have%20the%20freedom%20not%20to%20be%20partners%20in%20that%20crime.%20They%20are%20not%20our%20enemies.%20We%20do%20not%20hate%20any%20of%20these%20friends%20of%20ours%20in%20the%20media.%20They%20may%20have%20their%20compulsions.%20And%20nothing%20is%20permanent%2C%20if%20tomorrow%20they%20realise%20that%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20is%20not%20good%20for%20India%2C%20not%20good%20for%20the%20society%20we%20are%20all%20together%20in%20this%2C%20we%20will%20again%20start%20attending%20their%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20call%20it%20a%20ban.%20This%20can%20be%20called%20a%20non-cooperation%20movement.%20We%20are%20using%20a%20Gandhian%20method%20to%20exercise%20our%20freedom%20to%20not%20walk%20on%20those%20roads%20on%20which%20we%20are%20hurled%20garbage.%20We%20are%20just%20exercising%20our%20freedom%20and%20nothing%20else.%20All%20parties%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20we%20have%20to%20change%20our%20path%20and%20we%20will%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20ban%20or%20a%20boycott%20or%20a%20blacklist%2C%20this%20is%20a%20non-cooperation%20movement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20alliance%20took%20shape%20in%20June%2C%20the%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%20hostility%E2%80%9D%20faced%20by%20opposition%20parties%20during%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime.%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20indicated%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai%20meetings%20that%20a%20strategy%20to%20counter%20propagandist%20media%20will%20be%20discussed%20among%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMindset%20of%20%E2%80%98Emergency%E2%80%99%2C%20says%20BJP%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20move%20has%20evoked%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20accused%20the%20alliance%20of%20displaying%20a%20mindset%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Emergency%20under%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20when%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20was%20curtailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20that%20it%20severely%20opposes%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20derogatory%20mentality%20which%20hinders%20freedom%20of%20expression%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20of%20political%20parties%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98ghamandiya%E2%80%99%20alliance%20to%20boycott%20some%20journalists%20shows%20their%20mentality%20of%20the%20time%20of%20repressive%20Emergency.%20Today%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98ghamandiya%E2%80%99%20alliance%20is%20working%20with%20the%20same%20mindset%20of%20Emergency%20and%20vengeance%20against%20the%20media.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CINDIA%20alliance%20giving%20direct%20threat%20to%20the%20media%20is%20like%20gagging%20the%20media%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Friday%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Sambit%20Patra%20in%20New%20Delhi%20said%20that%20the%20names%20released%20by%20the%20opposition%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Chit%20list.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWas%20this%20a%20boycott%20list%20or%20a%20target%20list%3F%20Are%20they%20just%20being%20boycotting%20or%20are%20they%20being%20targeted%3F%20This%20is%20a%20hit%20list.%20There%20are%20some%20journalists%20who%20do%20not%20conduct%20debates%20so%20how%20will%20you%20send%20guests%20there%3F%20So%20why%20have%20their%20names%20been%20included%3F%20To%20target%20them.%20They%20will%20file%20FIRs%20against%20them%20and%20target%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20itself%20had%2C%20however%2C%20boycotted%20NDTV%20in%202014%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cmanufactured%20tweet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjp.org%2Fpressreleases%2Fpress-boycott-ndtv%5C%22%3Epress%20release%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20party%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTweet%20being%20manufactured%20by%20a%20channel%20in%20order%20to%20hurt%20BJP%20is%20unprecedented.%20BJP%20therefore%20has%20decided%20to%20keep%20away%20from%20panel%20discussions%20of%20NDTV%20for%20present.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENDTV%20had%20erroneously%20reported%20a%20tweet%20by%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20saying%20that%20if%20there%20is%20a%20Modi%20wave%20in%20India%2C%20then%20why%20is%20he%20(Modi)%20looking%20for%20a%20safe%20seat%20in%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Swaraj%E2%80%99s%20official%20handle%20had%20not%20made%20any%20such%20tweet%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F658110%2Fbjp-decides-to-boycott-ndtv-over-erroneous-tweet%5C%22%3E%20reported%20Scroll.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20official%20account%20of%20the%20channel%20and%20then%20senior%20editor%20Barkha%20Dutt%20apologised%20for%20the%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Dangerous%20precedent%2C%E2%80%99%20says%20NBDA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile