eRange%3DAnytime%26totalCount%3D611%26currentItemNo%3D7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epichealingeugene.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEPIC%20Healing%20Eugene%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Eugene%2C%20Oregon%20opened%20in%20June%20offering%20patients%20over%20the%20age%20of%2021%20a%20six-hour%20guided%20experience%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmagic-mushroom-depression-mental-health-treatment-psilocybin-therapy-tim-ferriss-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20psychedelic%20drug%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20better%20known%20as%20magic%20mushrooms.%20And%20it's%20proving%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20prescription%20or%20referral%20is%20required%2C%20but%20a%20%26quot%3Btrip%26quot%3B%20costs%20between%20%242%2C372%20and%20%243%2C400%20per%20person%2C%20although%20partner%20and%20group%20discounts%20are%20available.%20The%20service%20is%20not%20covered%20by%20health%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20first%20of%20several%20state-regulated%20centers%20to%20open%20in%20Oregon%20since%20the%20state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foregon-first-ever-state-to-legalize-psilocybin-for-therapeutic-use-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enarrowly%20approved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20use%20of%20psilocybin%20for%20therapeutic%20use%20in%202020.%20Many%20of%20those%20who%20have%20signed%20up%20report%20experiencing%20suicidal%20depression%20and%20PTSD%2C%20per%20The%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplications%20were%20not%20being%20handled%20in%20order%20of%20receipt%20but%20in%20a%20more%20ad-hoc%20fashion%20because%20its%20capacity%20was%20limited%2C%20Cathy%20Rosewell%20Jonas%20of%20the%20center%20says%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj3HyWd3ceq0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20video%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20years%20establishing%20reg