p%3EIn%201987%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20started%20working%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fpersonal_life_story%2Fpersonal-life-story%2F%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Secretary%20of%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20party%20won%20a%20majority%20in%20Gujarat%20in%201995%2C%20and%20he%20rose%20quickly%20up%20the%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%202001%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20assumed%20his%20first%20constitutional%20role%20when%20he%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat.%20Ever%20since%20that%20date%2C%20he%20has%20continued%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20an%20elected%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20not%20only%20the%20longest-serving%20non-Congress%20Prime%20Minister%20but%20also%20has%20the%20longest%20tenure%20as%20head%20of%20an%20elected%20government%2C%20which%20includes%20his%20term%20of%20more%20than%2012%20years%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20among%20all%20Prime%20Ministers%20the%20country%20has%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20decimated%20all%20opposition%20and%20swept%20the%20election%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20party%20to%20win%20a%20majority%20in%20over%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20PM%20Modi%20served%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20for%2013%20years%2C%20since%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20second%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20about%20to%20finish%20next%20year%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20still%20towers%20over%20Indian%20politics%20and%20much%20of%20the%20country's%20political%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694867760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F2jkp4vag_narendra-modi-ani_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarendra-modis-73rd-birthday-a-look-back-at-his-life-and-career-4395844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202014%2C%20t