%20the%20Environment%20Ministry%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sanctuary%20is%20expected%20to%20receive%20them%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Cheetah%20Action%20Plan%20that%20Kuno%20has%20a%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20about%2020%20cheetahs.%20Right%20now%2C%20there%20are%2015%20cheetahs%20including%20a%20cub%2C%20and%20when%20we%20will%20bring%20the%20next%20batch%20of%20cheetahs%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20will%20be%20at%20some%20other%20place.%20We%20are%20preparing%20two%20such%20sites%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20one%20is%20the%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Sanctuary%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20Nauradehi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20site%20preparation%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20is%20going%20on%20in%20full%20swing%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20expecting%20that%20it%20will%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20end%20of%20November%20or%20December.%20Once%20we%20get%20the%20report%20of%20completion%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20go%20to%20the%20site%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20evaluate%20it%20from%20all%20preparation%20points%20of%20view.%20And%20after%20December%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20take%20a%20call%20on%20bringing%20cheetahs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYadav%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20challenges%20encountered%20during%20the%20first%20year%20of%20managing%20cheetahs%20in%20India%20was%20the%20unexpected%20development%20of%20winter%20coats%20by%20certain%20cheetahs%20during%20the%20summer%20and%20monsoon%20season.%20This%20was%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20African%20winter%20from%20June%20to%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20even%20African%20experts%20did%20not%20anticipate%20this%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20a%20total%20of%2020%20animals%20were%20imported%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20to%20Kuno%20in%20two%20batches%20%E2%80%93%20one%20in%20September%20last%20year%20and%20the%20sec