quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20their%20direct%20reports%20in%20a%20lurch%2C%20since%20managers%20have%20such%20a%20large%20impact%20on%20someone's%20role%3A%20workflows%2C%20productivity%2C%20support%2C%20growth%2C%20and%20more.%20Bonita%20Eby%2C%20a%20burnout%20prevention%20consultant%2C%20told%20me%20that's%20why%20it's%20important%20to%20remove%20the%20taboo%20%E2%80%94%20including%20for%20managers%20%E2%80%94%20of%20saying%20%26quot%3BI%20need%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20with%20multiple%20experts%20about%20signs%20that%20your%20manager%20is%20burnt%20out%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFear.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BWe%20often%20see%20that%20when%20people%20are%20going%20through%20burnout%2C%20they%20become%20fearful%2C%20because%20they're%20experiencing%20such%20vast%20amounts%20of%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20Eby%20said.%20Fear%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20anxiety%20all%20go%20through%20the%20same%20nervous%20pathway%2C%20she%20said%2C%20so%20a%20burnt-out%20manager%20could%20be%20working%20in%20survival%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisengagement.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESood%20said%20this%20can%20manifest%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%3A%20silly%20errors%2C%20delayed%20or%20incomplete%20responses%2C%20irritability%2C%20or%20missing%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreating%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20people%20are%20experiencing%20burn%20out%2C%20Eby%20told%20me%20they%20can%20begin%20to%20create%20conflicts.%20In%20a%20manager%2C%20this%20can%20look%20like%20inappropriate%20language%20or%20off-colored%20jokes%2C%20which%20can%20put%20employees%20in%20a%20scary%20and%20uncomfortable%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisconnect%20from%20goals.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20manager's%20goals%20and%20the%20staff%20goals%20don't%20meet%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20and%20it's%20reflective%20in%20the%20inefficiency%20that%20gets%20built%20into%20a%20day's%2