0been%20accused%20of%20corruption%20over%20the%20procurement%20of%20military%20equipment%2C%20reports%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20said%20China's%20defense%20minister%20Li%20Shangfu%20was%20under%20investigation%20by%20authorities%20and%20had%20likely%20been%20removed%20from%20his%20position%20after%20he%20was%20taken%20away%20for%20questioning%20by%20authorities%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-defense-minister-has-been-removed-from-post-u-s-officials-say-ae0761f4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20Chinese%20military%20said%20the%20defense%20minister%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fus-diplomat-questions-whether-chinese-defence-minister-under-house-arrest-2023-09-15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuspected%20of%20corruption%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20procuring%20military%20equipment.%20A%20further%20eight%20officials%20from%20the%20government's%20military%20procurement%20unit%2C%20which%20General%20Li%20led%20from%202017%20to%202022%2C%20are%20under%20investigation%2C%20two%20sources%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20unexplained%20disappearances%20of%20high-ranking%20Chinese%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeign%20minister%20Qin%20Gang%20vanished%20from%20public%20view%20for%20a%20month%20in%20June%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F25%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fqin-gang-china-foreign-minister.html%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20replaced%20by%20Wang%20Yi%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20two%20months%20after%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20China's%20president%2C%20also%20replaced%20two%20of%20his%20most%20senior%20military%20commanders%20who%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20country's%20nuclear%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20official%20told%20The%20Journal%20that%20General%20Li's%20dismissal%20indicated%20problems%20with%20Xi's%20years-long%20campaign%20to%20reform%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%2C%20China's%20military.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20PLA's%20enduring%20problems%20may%20be%20too%20big%20for%20Xi%20to%20solve%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20real%20impact%20on%20the%20PLA's%20ability%20to%20achieve%20what%20he%20wants%20them%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20corruption%20in%20the%20PLA%20runs%20deep%20enough%20for%20this%20to%20be%20a%20factor.%20And%20we%20know%20it's%20had%20a%20profound%20effect%20on%20what%20they're%20able%20to%20do%2C%20and%20how%20they%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESu%20Tzu-yun%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20the%20Chinese%20military%20from%20the%20Institute%20for%20National%20Defense%20and%20Security%20Research%2C%20a%20Taiwan-funded%20think-tank%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F15%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fxi-china-military-general-li-shangfu.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20investigation%20signaled%20a%20%26quot%3Bloss%20of%20face%26quot%3B%20for%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20who%20had%20appointed%20General%20Li%20to%20the%20post%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20force%20him%20from%20power%2C%20but%20it%20will%20erode%20his%20prestige%20as%20ruler%2C%26quot%3B%20Su%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Li%2C%2065%2C%20has%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20for%20almost%20three%20weeks%2C%20and%20he%20canceled%20a%20scheduled%20meeting%20he%20was%20due%20to%20attend%20in%20Vietnam%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fchinas-defence-minister-not-seen-w