0of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20attacks%20primarily%20used%20air-launched%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20such%20as%20the%20AS-23a%20Kodiak%2C%20the%20UK%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20caused%20huge%20damage%20to%20Ukraine's%20power%20system%2C%20and%20the%20country%20is%20still%20working%20to%20repair%20infrastructure%2C%20gas%20storage%2C%20and%20other%20measures%20to%20counter%20further%20strikes%20this%20winter%2C%20according%20to%20the%20think%20tank%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlanticcouncil.org%2Fblogs%2Fukrainealert%2Fwinter-is-coming-is-ukraines-power-grid-ready-for-new-russian-attacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Atlantic%20Council.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20better%20prepared%20this%20year%2C%20but%20a%20few%20well-aimed%20strikes%20could%20again%20cause%20an%20energy%20crisis%2C%20the%20think%20tank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-preparing-attack-ukraine-energy-infrastructure-this-winter-uk-intel-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694861998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65057f01f05aa00019bd93e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-preparing-attack-ukraine-energy-infrastructure-this-winter-uk-intel-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20could%20generate%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20stockpile%20of%20cruise%20missiles%20to%20attack%20Ukraine%20this%20winter%2C%20says%20UK%20intel%2C%20with%20energy%20infrastructure%20a%20target.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-preparing-attack-ukraine-energy-infrastructure-this-winter-uk-intel-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%