0Stalin's%20comments%2C%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20a%20set%20of%20'eternal%20duties'%20which%20can%20be%20gathered%20from%20multiple%20sources%20relating%20to%20Hinduism%20or%20those%20practising%20the%20Hindu%20way%20of%20life%2C%20and%20includes%20%26quot%3Bthe%20duty%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20duty%20to%20the%20King%2C%20King's%20duty%20to%20his%20people%2C%20duty%20to%20one's%20parents%20and%20Gurus%2C%20care%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20whole%20lot%20of%20other%20duties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20N%20Seshasayee%20said%20in%20his%20order%20on%20September%2015%20that%20the%20court%20is%20conscious%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20very%20vociferous%2C%20and%20at%20time%20noisy%20debates%20on%20pro%20and%20anti%20Sanatana%20Dharma%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20court%20could%20not%20help%20pondering%20over%20with%20genuine%20concern%20for%20what%20is%20going%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20when%20free%20speech%20is%20exercised%20in%20matters%20pertaining%20to%20religion%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20for%20one%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20is%20injured%20and%20%26quot%3Bfree%20speech%20cannot%20be%20hate%20speech%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomewhere%2C%20an%20idea%20appears%20to%20have%20gained%20ground%20that%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20all%20about%2C%20and%20only%20about%2C%20promoting%20casteism%20and%20untouchability.%20Untouchability%20in%20a%20country%20of%20equal%20citizens%20cannot%20be%20tolerated%2C%20and%20even%20if%20it%20is%20seen%20as%20permitted%20somewhere%20within%20the%20principles%20of%20'Sanatana%20dharma'%2C%20it%20still%20cannot%20have%20a%20space%20to%20stay%2C%20since%20Article%2017%20of%20the%20Constitution%20has%20declared%20that%20untouchability%20has%20been%20abolished.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20fundamental%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20under%20Art.%2051A(a)%2C%20it%20is%20the%20fundamental%20duty%20of%20every%20citizen%20to%2C%20'abide%20by%20the%20Constitution%20and%20respect%20its%20ideals%20and%20institutions..'.%20%C2%A0Therefore%2C%20untouchability%2C%20either%20within%20or%20outside%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20Constitutional%2C%20though%20sadly%20it%20still%20exits%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20referred%20to%20the%20arguments%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20petitioner%20Elangovan%20and%20said%20he%20had%20submitted%20with%20considerable%20force%20that%20nowhere%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20either%20approves%20or%20promotes%20untouchability%2C%20and%20it%20only%20insists%20the%20practitioners%20of%20Hinduism%20to%20treat%20all%20equally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20religious%20practices%20move%20with%20time%2C%20some%20bad%20or%20evil%20practices%20may%20un-noticingly%20creep%20into%20it.%20They%20are%20the%20weeds%20required%20to%20be%20removed.%20But%20why%20should%20the%20crop%20be%20chopped%3F'%20-%20This%2C%20in%20short%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20submissions%20of%20the%20learned%20counsel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20noted.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20challenging%20a%20circular%20issued%20by%20a%20local%20government%20college%20asking%20girl%20students%20to%20share%20their%20thoughts%20on%20the%20topic%20'Opposition%20to%20Sanatana'%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20DMK%20founder%20CN%20Annadurai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20plea%20after%20noting%20that%20the%20circular%20had%20already%20been%20withdrawn%20by%20the%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Court%20is%20conscious%20to%20the%20very%20vociferous%2C%20and%20at%20time%20noisy%20debates%20on%20pro%20and%20anti%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20It%20has%20also%20broadly%20understood%20Sanatana%20Dharama%20as%20a%20set%20of%20'eternal%20duties'%2C%20and%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20traced%20to%20one%20specific%20literature%2C%20but%20has%20to%20be%20gathered%20from%20multiple%20sources%20which%2C%20either%20relate%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20or%20which%20those%20who%20practice%20the%20Hindu%20way%20of%20life%2C%20have%20come%20to%20accept%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20includes%20the%20duty%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20duty%20to%20the%20King%2C%20King's%20duty%20to%20his%20people%2C%20duty%20to%20one's%20parents%20and%20Gurus%2C%20care%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20other%20duties.%20If%20the%20topic%20chosen%20by%20the%20impugned%20circular%20is%20now%20tested%20on%20the%20plane%20of%20these%20duties%2C%20it%20would%20then%20mean%20that%20all%20these%20duties%20are%20liable%20to%20be%20destroyed.%20Should%20not%20a%20citizen%20love%20his%20country%3F%20Is%20he%20not%20under%20a%20duty%20to%20serve%20his%20nation%3F%20Should%20not%20the%20parents%20be%20cared%3F%20With%20genuine%20concern%20for%20what%20is%20going%20round%2C%20this%20Court%20could%20not%20help%20pondering%20over%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20is%20conscious%20that%20every%20citizen%20has%20a%20fundamental%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20is%20inalienable%2C%20it%20is%20also%20important%20to%20underscore%20that%20one%20is%20adequately%20informed%2C%20as%20it%20adds%20value%20to%20what%20is%20spoken.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20forgotten%20that%20the%20Constitutional%20framers%20have%20very%20consciously%20not%20made%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20as%20an%20absolute%20right.%20They%20have%20restricted%20it%20with%20Article%2019(2)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20Article%2025%20has%20granted%20all%20citizens%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20practice%20any%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20religion%20is%20founded%20on%20faith%2C%20and%20faith%20by%20nature%20accommodates%20irrationality.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20free%20speech%20is%20exercised%20in%20matters%20pertaining%20to%20religion%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20for%20one%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20is%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20free%20speech%20cannot%20be%20hate%20speech%2C%20as%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20cautioned.%20The%20users%20of%20free%20speech%20must%20not%20ignore%20to%20factor%20these%20aspects%20while%20exercising%20their%20right.%20If%20this%20is%20ignored%2C%20the%20course%20of%20any%20debate%20will%20get%20derailed%2C%20and%20the%20objective%20behind%20it%20will%20lose%20significance%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20would%20be%20appreciable%2C%20if%20free%20speech%20encourages%20dispassionate%2C%20and%20healthy%20public%20debates%2C%20and%20helps%20society%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20free%20speech%20is%20seen%20exercised%20these%20days%3F%20If%20the%20free%20speech%20made%20through%20the%20social%20media%20is%20taken%20as%20a%20basis%2C%20anyone%20who%20has%20little%20to%20do%20with%20science%2C%20or%20rocket%2C%20or%20space%2C%20will%20be%20lecturing%20on%20rocket%20science.%20While%20this%20is%20also%20accommodated%20within%20the%20right%20to%20free%20speech%2C%20yet%20it%20may%20be%20helpful%20to%20gain%20some%20attention%2C%20and%20may%20not%20take%20it%20beyond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20appreciable%2C%20if%20free%20speech%20encourages%20dispassionate%2C%20and%20healthy%20public%20debates%2C%20and%20help%20the%20society%20to%20move%20forward%2C%20along%20the%20lines%20which%20the%20Constitution%20envisages.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20every%20citizen%20traces%20his%20existence%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20hence%20it%20is%20his%20duty%20to%20abide%20by%20its%20values%2C%20its%20ethos%2C%20and%20to%20hold%20an%20uncompromising%20abidance%20to%20its%20spirits.%20This%20should%20not%20be%20forgotten.%