hoomi%20convention%20centre%20in%20Delhi's%20Dwarka%20on%20Sunday.%20One%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20MICE%20(Meetings%2C%20Incentives%2C%20Conferences%2C%20and%20Exhibitions)%20facilities%2C%20YashoBhoomi%20is%20spread%20across%20an%20area%20of%208.9%20lakh%20square%20metre%20and%20has%20a%20total%20built%20up%20area%20of%20over%201.8%20lakh%20square%20metre.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Visuals%20of%20'YashoBhoomi'%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20dedicate%20to%20the%20nation%20at%20Dwarka%20on%2017th%20September%20in%20Delhi.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fj5D86ruHAv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fj5D86ruHAv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1702924525459898441%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20centre%2C%20also%20called%20India%20International%20Convention%20and%20Expo%20Centre%2C%20has%2015%20convention%20rooms%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20main%20auditorium%2C%20the%20Grand%20Ballroom%2C%20and%2013%20meeting%20rooms%20that%20can%20hold%20up%20to%2011%2C000%20delegates%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20main%20auditorium%2C%20there%20is%20seating%20arrangement%20for%206%2C000%20guests.%20The%20seating%20system%20is%20automated%20which%20allows%20the%20floor%20to%20be%20a%20flat%20floor%20or%20an%20auditorium%20style%20tiered%20seating.%20The%20interior%20has%20been%20given%20premium%20finish%20with%20wooden%20floors%20and%20acoustic%20wall%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Grand%20Ballroom%20features%20a%20petal%20ceiling%20and%20can%20host%20about%202%2C500%20delegates.%20The%20extended%20open%20area%20offers%20more%20space%20for%20around%20