reak%20were%20appreciated%20by%20the%20central%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkozhikode%2Fkerala-govt-working-to-identify-area-source-of-first-nipah-virus-case%2Farticleshow%2F103714427.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TikTok%20slapped%20with%20a%20%24368%20million%20fine%20in%20Europe%20for%20failing%20to%20protect%20children's%20privacy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TikTok%20app%20logo%20shown%20on%20someone's%20phone%20being%20held%20in%20front%20of%20a%20keyboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65057a14cd637c0019c64988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TikTok%20logo%20displayed%20on%20the%20screen%20of%20a%20smartphone.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEuropean%20regulators%20hit%20social%20media%20platform%20TikTok%20with%20a%20%24368%20million%20fine%20for%20lapses%20in%20children's%20privacy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20first%20time%20the%20video-sharing%20app%20has%20been%20penalized%20under%20Europe's%20data%20privacy%20rules.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20TikTok's%20head%20of%20privacy%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20the%20decision's%20criticisms%20are%20no%20longer%20relevant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20regulators%20imposed%20a%20%24368%20million%20fine%20on%20TikTok%2C%20the%20first%20time%20the%20popular%20video-sharing%20platform%20has%20faced%20penalties%20for%20violating%20the%20EU's%20strict%20data%20privacy%20regulations%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FTechnology%2FwireStory%2Ftiktok-hit-368-million-fine-europes-strict-data-103216613%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Associated%20Press%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fine%20was%20issued%20by%20Ireland's%20Data%20Protection%20Commission%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20the%20leading%20privacy%20regulator%20for%20major%20tech%20companies%20based%20in%20Dublin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20found%20significant%20lapses%20in%20the%20protection%20of%20children's%20privacy%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20findings%20was%20that%20the%20default%20settings%20for%20teen%20accounts%20made%20them%20public%2C%20allowing%20unrestricted%20access%20for%20anyone%20to%20view%20and%20comment%20on%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20also%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20pairing%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20designed%20to%20let%20parents%20manage%20children's%20account%20settings%2C%20was%20not%20strict%20enough.%20This%20allowed%20adults%20to%20enable%20direct%20messaging%20for%20users%20aged%2016%20and%2017%20without%20their%20consent%2C%20potentially%20compromising%20their%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20also%20nudged%20teenage%20users%20toward%20more%20%26quot%3Bprivacy%20intrusive%26quot%3B%20options%20during%20the%20sign-up%20and%20video%20posting%20process%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20disagreed%20with%20the%20regulatory%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20argued%20that%20many%20of%20the%20features%20and%20settings%20criticized%20by%20the%20regulator%20had%20been%20addressed%20before%20the%20investigation%20began%20in%202021%2C%20AP%20reported.%20They%20said%20they%20had%20already%20made%20accounts%20for%20users%20under%2016%20private%20by%20default%20and%20had%20disabled%20direct%20messaging%20for%20users%20aged%2013-15.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElaine%20Fox%2C%20TikTok's%20head%20of%20privacy%20for%20Europe%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.tiktok.com%2Fen-eu%2Fresponse-data-protection-commission%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20the%20decision's%20criticisms%20are%20no%20longer%20relevant%20as%20a%20result%20of%20measures%20we%20introduced%20at%20the%20start%20of%202021.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20that%20TikTok%20has%20been%20fined%20over%20data%20protection%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20privacy%20regulators%20in%20the%20UK%20issued%20a%20%C2%A312.7%20million%20(%2415.7%20million)%20fine%20to%20TikTok%20in%20April%20for%20mishandling%20children's%20data%20and%20breaching%20protections%20for%20young%20users'%20personal%20information%2C%20AP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-fined-368m-in-europe-for-failing-to-protect-childrens-privacy-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694860501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65057a14cd637c0019c64988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-fined-368m-in-europe-for-failing-to-protect-childrens-privacy-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TikTok%20has%20been%20hit%20with%20a%20%24368%20million%20fine%20by%20European%20regulators%20for%20breaching%20data%20privacy%20rules.%20The%20platform%20was%20criticized%20for%20reportedly%20failing%20to%20protect%20children's%20privacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen%2CAssociated%20Press)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-fined-368m-in-europe-for-failing-to-protect-childrens-privacy-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20next%20big%20challenge%20for%20bosses%3A%20Find%20the%20perfect%20balance%20between%20rigid%209-to-5ers%20and%20employees%20who%20want%20a%20more%20flexible%20schedule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Remote%20work%20coronavirus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ee7a4e22618b920a731a934%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20video%20producer%20works%20from%20his%20at-home%20studio%20to%20conduct%20remote%20interviews%20with%20talent%20on%20April%2019%2C%202020%20in%20Franklin%20Square%2C%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EEric%20Stringer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAround%20half%20of%20American%20workers%20want%20a%20more%20rigid%2C%209-to-5%20job%2C%20per%20a%20recent%20Gallup%20poll.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBosses%2C%20however%2C%20think%20many%20more%20employees%20want%20flexibility%20with%20work%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20mismatch%20could%20amount%20to%20lower%20engagement%20and%20higher%20burnout.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20like%20to%20weave%20chores%20and%20personal%20time%20throughout%20your%20workday%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20being%20online%20a%20little%20later%20in%20the%20day%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20do%20you%20prefer%20to%20focus%20only%20on%20work%20from%20nine%20to%20five%20and%20then%20log%20off%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20answer%20could%20determine%20if%20you're%20a%20%26quot%3Bblender%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20who%20wants%20to%20have%20the%20flexibility%20to%20mix%20work%20and%20outside%20activities%20throughout%20the%20day%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bsplitter%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20who%20wants%20better-defined%20boundaries%20between%20work%20and%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20two%20types%20of%20workers%20were%20defined%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fworkplace%2F405392%2Fsplitters-blenders-two-different-relationships-work.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGallup%20in%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202022%2C%20and%20is%20important%20to%20know%20which%20you%20are%20so%20you%20can%20decide%20what%20kind%20of%20schedule%20works%20best%20for%20you%20and%20communicate%20that%20to%20your%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fworkplace%2F510656%2Femployees-schedule-leaders-think.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20Gallup%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20last%20Friday%20found%20a%20disconnect%20between%20want%20workers%20want%20and%20what%20bosses%20think%20they%20want.%20Researchers%20told%20Insider%20the%20solution%20to%20that%20is%20simple%3A%20talk%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20employees%20have%20probably%20never%20been%20asked%20how%20they%20prefer%20to%20work%2C%20and%20yet%20we%20know%20that%20when%20workers%20can%20work%20in%20a%20way%20that%20matches%20their%20preferred%20style%2C%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20engaged%20and%20less%20likely%20to%20burn%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Pendell%2C%20senior%20workplace%20science%20editor%20at%20Gallup%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGallup%20found%20that%20workers%20are%20roughly%20split%20between%20the%20splitter%20and%20blender%20camps.%20But%20in%20a%20survey%20of%20Fortune%20500%20chief%20human%20resource%20offices%2C%20they%20found%20a%20mismatch%20between%20what%20CHROs%20think%20employees%20want%20for%20their%20work%20schedule%20and%20what%20employees%20actually%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20white-collar%20employees%2C%2045%25%20are%20splitters.%20Only%2024%25%20of%20CHROs%20thought%20their%20white-collar%20staff%20wanted%20such%20a%20rigid%20schedule.%20The%20gap%20was%20closer%20for%20production%20and%20front-line%20employees%20though%20still%20sizable%20at%20eight%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlenders%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20made%20up%2055%25%20of%20the%20white-collar%20population%2C%20while%20managers%20thought%20they'd%20be%2076%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%20couple%20years%2C%20leaders%20have%20been%20working%20hard%20to%20woo%20remote%20workers%20back%20into%20the%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Pendell%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20likely%20put%20blender%20types%20in%20the%20forefront%20of%20their%20minds%2C%20even%20if%20blenders%20aren't%20necessarily%20the%20same%20as%20remote%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20suggests%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20employees%20want%20more%20defined%20work%20hours%20than%20their%20bosses%20anticipate.%20The%209-to-5%20workday%20common%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic%20may%20be%20making%20a%20comeback%2C%20and%20many%20bosses%20are%20unaware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20workers%20want%20to%20log%20off%20at%205%20p.m.%20and%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20their%20boss%20messaging%20them%20about%20a%20project%20or%20their%20company%20hosting%20happy%20hours.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20may%20want%20to%20work%20a%20few%20hours%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20spend%20the%20afternoon%20with%20family%2C%20and%20then%20come%20back%20and%20finish%20the%20day's%20work%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreferring%20remote%20work%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20you're%20a%20blender%2C%20Pendell%20said.%20With%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20hybrid%20roles%20and%20a%20shift%20away%20from%20purely%20remote%20work%20opportunities%2C%20many%20workers%20in%20hybrid%20positions%20still%20desire%20boundaries%20and%20focus%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20managers%20don't%20account%20for%20the%20work%20style%20preferences%20of%20their%20workers%2C%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20mismatches%20that%20can%20harm%20an%20organization's%20productivity.%20For%20instance%2C%20this%20could%20lower%20engagement%20and%20accelerate%20burnout%20and%20turnover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20may%20feel%20like%20nobody%20at%20work%20gets%20them%20as%20a%20person.%20It%20can%20feel%20like%20trying%20to%20be%20someone%20you're%20not%2C%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Pendell%20said.%20That's%20a%20recipe%20for%20burnout%20and%20quitting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPendell%20said%20that%20managers%20may%20assume%20that%20because%20they%20see%20their%20work%20style%20as%20ideal%20for%20the%20workplace%2C%20their%20staff%20also%20prefer%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20known%20for%20a%20long%20time%20that%20workers%20today%20desire%20flexibility%20and%20autonomy%20in%20their%20work%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20large%20share%20of%20employees%20who%20want%20clear%20boundaries%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Pendell%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20cause%20us%20to%20think%20deeper%20about%20what%20people%20mean%20when%20they%20say%20flexibility%20and%20autonomy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManagers%2C%20though%2C%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20ask%20themselves%20how%20they%20can%20position%20their%20talent%20such%20that%20everyone%20is%20performing%20at%20their%20best%2C%20Pendell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManagers%20should%20understand%20themselves%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Pendell%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20should%20recognize%20that%20their%20preferred%20way%20of%20working%20is%20a%20style%2C%20and%20that%20other%20styles%20can%20be%20equally%20productive%20and%20engaged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20looking%20to%20go%20back%20to%20a%209-to-5%20schedule%20after%20trying%20more%20flexible%20work%3F%20Do%20you%20still%20prefer%20having%20more%20flexible%20hours%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20nsheidlower%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-life-balance-expectations-flexible-work-boundaries-manager-boss-challenges-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694860201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65046702b8708d001927b60d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-life-balance-expectations-flexible-work-boundaries-manager-boss-challenges-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22American%20workers%20are%20split%20between%20dividing%20or%20blending%20work%20and%20personal%20life%2C%20but%20bosses%20think%20many%20more%20workers%20prefer%20blending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-life-balance-expectations-flexible-work-boundaries-manager-boss-challenges-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Bloc%20Cancelled%20Rally%20As%20People%20Are%20Angry%20They%20Insulted%20Sanatana%3A%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20rally%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20capital%20Bhopal%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%20has%20been%20cancelled%2C%20top%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20said%20today.%20Discussions%20regarding%20the%20rally%20are%20going%20on%20with%20the%20Congress%20President%20and%20other%20partners%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20no%20final%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20on%20when%20and%20where%20it%20will%20now%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20claimed%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20cancelled%20its%20first%20rally%20as%20people%20are%20angry%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Binsulted%26quot%3B%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20anger%20of%20the%20public.%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20was%20insulted%20and%20was%20called%20dengue%20and%20Malaria.%20The%20people%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20will%20not%20tolerate%20this%20insult%20of%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20INDI%20alliance%20must%20understand%20that%20they%20have%20hurt%20our%20faith%20and%20this%20won't%20be%20tolerated%20at%20any%20cost.%20People%20of%20MP%20are%20angry%20and%20they%20(INDIA%20alliance)%20were%20scared%20therefore%20they%20cancelled%20their%20rally.%20The%20public's%20anger%20is%20against%20the%20INDI%20bloc%20and%20Congress.%20The%20public%20will%20not%20leave%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20no%20strength%20in%20the%20alliance's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20chaos%20within%20the%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20and%20people%20are%20fighting%20over%20whose%20photo%20is%20included%20in%20posters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20BJP%2C%20everyone%20is%20involved%20in%20working%20during%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20decided%20to%20hold%20their%20first%20joint%20public%20meeting%20in%20Bhopal%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%20and%20said%20the%20constituent%20parties%20would%20start%20seat-sharing%20talks%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20Coordination%20Committee%20of%20INDIA%20was%20held%20at%20NCP%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20residence%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%20and%20Mr%20Surjewala%20were%20addressing%20the%20media%20in%20Bhopal%20regarding%20their%20party's%20state-wide%20'Jan%20Akrosh%20Yatra'%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20public%20anger%20march%2C%20ahead%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20Jan%20Akrosh%20Yatras%20of%20the%20Congress%20will%20start%20on%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20which%20is%20on%20September%2019%2C%20the%20party%20said.%20They%20will%20cover%2011%2C400%20kilometres%20in%20all%20230%20assembly%20segments%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%2015%20days.%20The%20yatras%20will%20be%20led%20by%20senior%20leaders%2C%20including%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition%20(LoP)%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20Dr%20Govind%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20leaders%20who%20will%20lead%20the%20yatras%20include%20ex-union%20ministers%20Arun%20Yadav%2C%20Kantilal%20Bhuria%2C%20Suresh%20Pachouri%2C%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20member%20Kamleshwar%20Patel%2C%20ex-MP%20minister%20Jeetu%20Patwari%2C%20and%20former%20LoP%20Ajay%20Singh%20'Rahul'.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20who%20will%20be%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20Congress%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Congress%20national%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20for%20MP%2C%20Randeep%20Surjewala%2C%20pointed%20towards%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20was%20seated%20next%20to%20him.%20Though%20the%20party's%20top%20decision-making%20body%2C%20the%20CWC%2C%20will%20decide%20whether%20Kamal%20Nath%20will%20contest%20the%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Surjewala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694860200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fdm91dke8_congress-bhopal-presser_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-bhopal-rally-cancelled-new-date-and-location-soon-congress-4395408%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposed%20rally%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20capital%20Bhopal%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%20has%20been%20cancelled%2C%20top%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-bhopal-rally-cancelled-new-date-and-location-soon-congress-4395408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-bhopal-rally-cancelled-new-date-and-location-soon-congress-4395408%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-bhopal-rally-cancelled-new-date-and-location-soon-congress-4395408%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20learned%20social%20cues%20from%20reading%20books%20because%20he%20had%20no%20friends%20as%20a%20child%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227577%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20wearing%20a%20suit%20and%20raising%20one%20eyebrow%20talks%20to%20another%20CEO%20before%20a%20roundtable%20during%20the%206th%20edition%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BChoose%20France%26quot%3B%20Summit%20at%20the%20Chatea