aughton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdetroit-auto-show-highlights-new-cars-f-150-reveal-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mauritius%20Financial%20Regulator%20Revoked%20Licence%20of%20Firm%20Linked%20to%20Adani%20Investors%20in%20May%202022%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16195900%2Fadani-pti.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mauritian%20financial%20regulator%20Financial%20Services%20Commission%20(FSC)%20had%20in%20May%202022%20revoked%20the%20business%20and%20investment%20licences%20of%20Emerging%20India%20Fund%20Management%20Ltd%20(EIFM)%2C%20the%20controlling%20shareholder%20of%20two%20Mauritius-based%20funds%20that%20invested%20in%20publicly%20listed%20Adani%20companies%20and%20are%20now%20under%20investigation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmoney-laundering-laws-firm-linked-to-adani-investors-lost-licences-in-mauritius-8941826%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revocation%20of%20licence%20means%20EIFM%2C%20effectively%2C%20began%20winding%20down%20operations.%20And%20this%20happened%20eight%20months%20before%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20released%20its%20report%2C%20accusing%20the%20Adani%20Group%20of%20accounting%20fraud%20and%20stock%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FSC%20Enforcement%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20decision%20was%20based%20on%20EIFM%20allegedly%20breaching%20several%20provisions%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20corporate%20governance%20laws%2C%20noted%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FSC%20held%20that%20EIFM%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20breach%E2%80%9D%20of%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Financial%20Services%20Act%2C%20the%20Securities%20Act%2C%20the%20Financial%20Intelligence%20and%20Anti-Money%20Laundering%20Regulations%20(2003%20and%202018)%20and%20the%20Code%20on%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20and%20Terrorist%20Financing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20licence%20revocation%20notice%20is%20on%20the%20regulator%E2%80%99s%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20alleged%20breaches%20relate%20to%20non-compliance%20on%20maintaining%20records%20of%20clients%20and%20transactions%2C%20accounting%20and%20auditing%20standards%3B%20safeguards%20against%20dummy%20officers%3B%20corporate%20governance%20and%20the%20prescribed%20internal%20mechanism%20to%20identify%20risks%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20terrorist%20financing%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEIFM%20was%20held%20guilty%20of%20breaching%20both%20the%202003%20and%202018%20versions%20of%20Mauritius%E2%80%99s%20Financial%20Intelligence%20and%20Anti-Money%20Laundering%20Regulations%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20last%20available%20records%2C%20during%20March-April%202018%2C%20EIFM%E2%80%99s%20two%20Mauritius%20funds%20held%203.9%25%20of%20Adani%20Power%20Limited%2C%203.86%25%20of%20Adani%20Transmission%20Limited%2C%20and%2C%20at%20least%2C%201.73%25%20of%20Adani%20Enterprise%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20FSC%20told%3Cem%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noamphtml%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20licence%20is%20revoked%2C%20it%20is%20on%20a%20permanent%20basis.%20Following%20the%20revocation%E2%80%A6%20licensees%20are%20directed%20to%20initiate%20the%20necessary%20actions%20for%20the%20orderly%20dissolution%20of%20their%20business%20and%20the%20discharge%20of%20their%20liabilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20implication%20of%20the%20revocation%20of%20EIFM%E2%80%99s%20licences%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20comment%20on%20ma