e%20two%20closed%20boxes%20with%20glass%20lids%20containing%20the%20bodies%20into%20a%20green-screened%20studio%2C%20where%20Reuters%20had%20exclusive%20access%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20huddles%20around%20to%20get%20a%20better%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlien%20bodies%20share%20characteristics%20with%20humans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20appear%20ancient%20and%20share%20characteristics%20with%20humans%3A%20two%20eyes%2C%20a%20mouth%2C%20two%20arms%2C%20two%20legs.%20Maussan%20claims%20they%20were%20found%20around%202017%20in%20Peru%2C%20near%20the%20pre-Columbian%20Nazca%20Lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F6md8go5o_aliens_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20he%20can%20prove%20they%20are%20unlike%20anything%20known%20on%20Earth.%20On%20social%20media%20and%20in%20the%20hearing%2C%20he%20shared%20scientific%20analysis%20and%20study%20results%20he%20argues%20proves%20the%20bodies%20are%20about%201%2C000%20years%20old%20and%20not%20related%20to%20any%20known%20Earthly%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%2C%20described%20by%20Maussan%20as%20a%20female%2C%20was%20discovered%20to%20have%20eggs%20inside%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20that%20has%20happened%20to%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20Maussan%2C%2070%2C%20said%20of%20his%20crusade%20to%20bring%20awareness%20to%20the%20findings%2C%20sitting%20in%20his%20office%20that%20is%20heavily%20decorated%20with%20colorful%20alien-themed%20artwork%20and%20paraphernalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20this%20phenomenon%20is%20the%20only%20one%20that%20gives%20us%20the%20opportunity%20to%20unite%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElsa%20Tomasto-Cagigao%2C%20a%20respected%20Peruvian%20bio-anthropologist%2C%20is%20frustrated%20such%20claims%20are%20still%20being%20given%20publicity%2C%20citing%20similar%20alleged%20finds%20that%20were%20found%20to%20be%20frauds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20said%20before%20still%20stands%2C%20they%20are%20presenting%20the%20same%20rehash%20as%20always%20and%20if%20there%20are%20people%20that%20keep%20believing%20that%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20by%20phone.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20so%20crass%20and%20so%20simple%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20to%20add.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrevious%20such%20finds%20have%20been%20dismissed%20by%20the%20scientific%20community%20as%20mutilated%20mummies%20of%20pre-Hispanic%20children%2C%20sometimes%20combined%20with%20bits%20of%20animal%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENASA%20wants%20more%20information%20on%20'1%2C000-Year-Old%20alien%20bodies'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Spergel%2C%20former%20head%20of%20Princeton%20University's%20astrophysics%20department%20and%20chair%20of%20a%20NASA%20report%20into%20unidentified%20anomalous%20phenomena%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-you-have-what-nasa-said-about-alien-bodies-in-mexico-4391401%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuch%20samples%20should%20be%20made%20available%20for%20testing%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20world's%20scientific%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaussan%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20and%20in%20his%20presentation%20the%20results%20of%20DNA%20and%20carbon%20dating%20tests%20that%20he%20said%20he%20commissioned%20on%20%26quot%3Bthe%20beings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Mexican%20scientist%2C%20at%20the%20request%20of%20Reuters%2C%20reviewed%20the%20results%20and%20concluded%20they%20indicated%20normal%20life%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5