ill%20death%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sajida%2C%20Junaid%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManesar%20is%20one%20of%20the%2021%20accused%20in%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20Nasir%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Hamid%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20very%20happy%20today%20that%20Monu%20has%20finally%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20police.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20saw%20the%20Bharatpur%20SP%E2%80%99s%20(superintendent%20of%20police)%20comment%20on%20his%20arrest%2C%20and%20when%20his%20custody%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%2C%20I%20informed%20Nasir%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20his%20wife%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20ago%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Rajasthan%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(DGP)%2C%20Umesh%20Mishra%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20there%20is%20no%20direct%20involvement%20of%20Monu%20(Manesar)%20in%20this%20incident.%20His%20role%20is%20still%20being%20investigated%20in%20the%20background.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20views%20on%20the%20involvement%20of%20Monu%20Manesar%20in%20this%20case%2C%20Hamid%20alleged%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20the%20charge-sheet.%20Monu%20is%20involved%20in%20our%20brother%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20%E2%80%A6The%20charge-sheet%20has%20proof%20from%20his%20WhatsApp%20chat%20to%20call%20details%2C%20and%20he%20was%20directly%20involved%20in%20that%20%5Bthe%20murder%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fashok-gehlot-questions-haryana-cm-s-offer-to-help-arrest-monu-manesar-news-307820%5C%22%3Ehad%20alleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20Rajasthan%20Police%20had%20gone%20to%20Haryana%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20double%20murder%20case%2C%20it%20received%20no%20cooperation%20from%20the%20police%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20all%20changed%20for%20the%20families%20in%20these%20seven%20months%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJunaid%20was%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20for%20two%20families%3A%20his%20own%20and%20his%20brother%20Jafar.%20While%20Jafar%E2%80%99s%20family%20consists%20of%20seven%20children%2C%20Junaid%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20six.%20All%20of%20them%20depended%20on%20Junaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20our%20children%20used%20to%20go%20to%20school%2C%20but%20now%20how%20will%20I%20send%20them%20to%20school%3F%20I%20have%20no%20money%20and%20no%20source%20of%20earning.%20I%20had%20to%20take%20them%20out%20of%20school%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20studying%20in%20madrasa.%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20send%20them%20back%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sajida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJunaid%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20daughter%2C%20who%20is%2012%20years%20old%2C%20has%20been%20unwell%20and%20bed-ridden%20since%20she%20heard%20the%20news%20of%20Junaid%E2%80%99s%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20of%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20are%20still%20afraid%20to%20go%20out.%20They%20say%20they%20live%20in%20fear%20of%20getting%20attacked%20by%20Manesar%E2%80%99s%20gang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZahida%20Khan%2C%20the%20education%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecitizen.in%2Findia%2Fharyanas-nuh-district-remains-volatile-in-the-wake-of-junaid-nasir-deaths-894460%5C%22%3Ehad%20promised%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2020.5%20lakh%20each%20for%20both%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%E2%80%99s%20families.%20However%2C%20the%20families%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20they%20are%20yet%20to%20receive%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20from%20the%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Deeg%20SP%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMonu%20was%20part%20of%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir.%20He%20had%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20first%20accused%20we%20arrested%2C%20Rinku%20Saini%2C%20through%20messages.%20He%20had%20the%20details%20of%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%E2%80%99s%20mobile%20numbers%20and%20their%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20number%20days%20before%20their%20deaths.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Ghatmeeka%20was%20in%20the%20Bharatpur%20district%2C%20but%20now%2C%20following%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fjaipur-news%2Frajasthan-government-announces-17-new-districts-and-redraws-jaipur-and-jodhpur-in-preparation-for-assembly-elections-101691154833164.html%5C%22%3Eannouncement%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2017%20new%20districts%2C%20it%20falls%20under%20the%20Deeg%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20has%20expressed%20disappointment%20over%20Manesar%E2%80%99s%20arrest.%20In%20a%20tweet%2C%20the%20right-wing%20outfit%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CInnocent%20cow%20devotee%20Monu%20Manesar%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20Rajasthan%20Police%2C%20whereas%20some%20time%20ago%2C%20Rajasthan%20Police%20had%20considered%20him%20innocent.%20Cow%20devotee%20Monu%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20elections.%20The%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20will%20help%20cow%20devotee%20Monu%20Manesar%20in%20every%20way%2C%20and%20if%20necessary%2C%20%5Bwe%5D%20will%20also%20protest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694847422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16122609%2Fimage-1318.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Feven-after-monu-manesars-arrest-junaid-and-nasirs-kin-continue-to-face-hardships-live-in-fear%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20families%20of%20the%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20justice%20for%20seven%20long%20months%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Ghatmeeka.%20The%20two%20men%20were%20allegedly%20attacked%20and%20abducted%20by%20a%20mob%20that%20later%20set%20them%20ablaze%2C%20alive%20in%20a%20car.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engag