20374.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-did-you-know-shah-rukh-khan-owns-a-substantial-portion-of-lunar-real-estate-known-as-the-sea-of-tranquility%2Farticleshow%2F103690213.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103690213.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIndia's%20recent%20achievement%20of%20successfully%20landing%20on%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20lunar%20ambitions.%20In%20an%20interesting%20twist%2C%20it%20is%20reported%20that%20Bollywood%20superstar%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20owns%20a%20portion%20of%20lunar%20real%20estate%20known%20as%20the%20'Sea%20of%20Tranquility.'%20Khan%20receives%20an%20annual%20certificate%20from%20the%20Lunar%20Republic%20Society%20confirming%20his%20ownership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20Special%20Director%20Rahul%20Navin%20Made%20Acting%20Chief%20as%20Sanjay%20Mishra%20Steps%20Down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16114632%2F194128-ipmkyzasrr-1694842960.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20finally%20found%20a%20replacement%20for%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20who%20stepped%20down%20as%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20by%20elevating%20special%20director%20Rahul%20Navin%20as%20its%20acting%20director.%20Navin%20will%20hold%20the%20charge%20till%20a%20regular%20director%20is%20appointed%20or%20until%20further%20orders%2C%20the%20late-night%20notification%20by%20a%20Department%20of%20Revenue%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavin%2C%20a%201993%20batch%20Indian%20Revenue%20Service%20(IRS)%20officer%2C%20joined%20the%20ED%20in%202019%20and%20was%20heading%20the%20Headquarters%20division%20of%20the%20ED%20that%20looks%20at%20all%20sensitive%20cases%20and%20intelligence%20inputs%20as%20well.%20Navin%20is%20the%20senior-most%20officer%20in%20the%20department%20and%20was%20said%20to%20enjoy%20a%20good%20working%20relationship%20with%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDirector%20ED%20is%20appointed%20as%20per%20the%20Central%20Vigilance%20Commission%20Act%2C%202003.%20The%20committee%20comprises%20two%20vigilance%20commissioners%20and%20the%20secretaries%20of%20home%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20the%20department%20of%20personnel%20and%20training%2C%20with%20the%20central%20vigilance%20commissioner%20as%20chairperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20July%2026%20after%20the%20court%20verdict%20of%20July%2011%20curtailed%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20to%20July%2031%20instead%20of%20November%2030.%20The%20Centre%20had%20said%20Mishra%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20till%20October%2015%20because%20a%20country%20review%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsk-mishra-enforcement-directorate-fatf-evaluation%5C%22%3EUN%E2%80%99s%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20India%20is%20currently%20underway.%20At%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20court%20had%20termed%20an%20earlier%20extension%20given%20to%20Mishra%20as%20being%20illegal%20and%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%202021%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMishra%20was%20appointed%20director%20in%202018%20for%20two%20years%20but%20just%20before%20his%20term%20ended%2C%20his%20terms%20of%20service%20were%20modified%20to%20extend%20his%20tenure%20for%20another%20year.%20However%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20while%20allowing%20the%20extension%20as%20being%20%E2%80%9Crarest%20of%20rare%E2%80%9D%2C%20had%20in%20September%202021%20said%20no%20more%20extensions%20were%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20in%20order%20to%20overcome%20the%202021%20SC%20judgement%2C%20went%20ahead%20and%20amended%20the%20Central%20Vigilance%20Commission%20Act%20amongst%20others%20to%20provide%20for%20yearly%20extensions%20up%20to%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years.%20Surprisingly%2C%20on%20July%2011%2C%20when%20the%20court%20finally%20put%20its%20foot%20down%2C%20the%20government%20again%20moved%20court%20and%20managed%20to%20bargain%20another%20month%20and%20a%20half%20for%20Mishra%20citing%20a%20FATF%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FATF%20is%20an%20international%20terror-financing%20watchdog.%20At%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20government%20simply%20said%20the%20review%20is%20at%20a%20critical%20stage.%20It%20omitted%20to%20mention%20that%20it%20began%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20will%20continue%20up%20to%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20well%20past%20the%20November%202023%20retirement%20date%20that%20the%20government%20had%20in%20mind%20for%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20told%20the%20court%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20extremely%20essential%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20is%20in%20the%20state%20of%20full%20readiness%20during%20this%20period%20till%20on-site%20(visit%20in%20November.)%20During%20this%20period%2C%20agencies%20are%20often%20required%20to%20provide%20responses%2C%20statistics%2C%20case%20studies%2C%20etc.%2C%20in%20short%20spans%20of%20time%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20understanding%20to%20assessment%20team%E2%80%A6For%20this%20purpose%2C%20guidance%20and%20leadership%20at%20a%20very%20senior%20level%20is%20required%E2%80%A6The%20intricacies%20of%20complex%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20may%20also%20need%20to%20be%20explained%20to%20them%20which%20can%20be%20done%20only%20by%20a%20person%20with%20hands-on%20experience%E2%80%A6The%20present%20Director%2C%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20documents%20%E2%80%A6since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%202020%2C%20accordingly%2C%20his%20continuation%20in%20this%20ardous%20and%20delicate%20process%20is%20essential%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20come%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3Eserious%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20what%20is%20considered%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftracking-the-ed-case-by-case-puzzling-questions-emerge-in-its-handling-of-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3Ewitch%20hunting%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20opposition%20with%20its%20unbridled%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20face%20of%20criticism%2C%20the%20ED%20maintains%20that%20it%20has%20a%20stellar%20track%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20website%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20a%20conviction%20rate%20of%2096%25%2C%20politicians%20comprise%20only%203%25%20of%20all%20cases%20and%20search%20warrants%20were%20issued%20in%208.99%25%20of%20the%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98conviction%20rate%E2%80%99%20is%20based%20on%2024%20out%20of%2025%20cases%20in%20which%20a%20PMLA%20trial%20was%20completed.%20IANS%20quoting%20finance%20ministry%20sources%20reports%20that%20between%202018-19%20and%202021-22%2C%20cases%20registered%20by%20ED%20rose%20by%20505%25%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2F505-rise-in-cases-registered-by-ed-since-2018-1205886.html%5C%22%3Efrom%20195%20cases%20in%202018-19%2C%20to%201%2C180%20in%202021-22%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20number%20of%20searches%20the%20ED%20conducted%20rose%20by%20a%20huge%202%2C555%25%20between%202004-14%20and%202014-22.%20As%20per%20the%20finance%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%2C%20112%20searches%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20ED%20between%202004-14%20resulting%20in%20attachment%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20worth%20Rs%205%2C346%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ED%20maintains%20its%20track%20record%20is%20stellar%2C%20questions%20regarding%20the%20role%20of%20the%20agency%20remain%20unanswered.%20For%20instance%2C%C2%A0how%20many%20cases%20has%20the%20investigation%20been%20completed%20so%20the%20trial%20can%20commence%3F%20How%20many%20cases%20have%20been%20registered%20and%20closed%20by%20way%20of%20discharge%20or%20quashing%20or%20acquittal%3F%C2%A0How%20many%20accused%20have%20been%20discharged%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20filed%20in%20court%3F%C2%A0Of%20the%20properties%20attached%2C%20how%20many%20have%20been%20confiscated%20by%20the%20ED%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20come%20in%20for%20a%20severe%20dressing%20down%20from%20the%20lower%20courts%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20extraordinary%20pace%20with%20which%20the%20ED%20arrests%20%5Ban%5D%20accused%20becomes%20not%20even%20a%20snail%E2%80%99s%20pace%20in%20conducting%20trials%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mumbai%20sessions%20judge%20M.G.%20Deshpande%20had%20said%20in%20the%20Patra%20Chawl%20order%20involving%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20applicant%20files%20bail%20applications%2C%20the%20ED%20takes%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20weeks%20or%20more%20to%20file%20their%20reply%E2%80%A6in%20every%20matter%2C%20it%20is%20noticed%20that%2C%20ED%20takes%20very%2C%20very%20long%20time%20to%20reply%20%5Bto%5D%20the%20simple%20applications%20filed%20by%20any%20accused.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20that%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20not%20completed%20a%20trial%20in%20a%20single%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20ED%20not%20accountable%20for%20such%20modus%20operandi%20availed%20by%20them%20in%20not%20beginning%20and%20concluding%20a%20single%20trial%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694845692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16114632%2F194128-ipmkyzasrr-1694842960.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fed-special-director-rahul-navin-appointed-as-acting-chief-as-sanjay-mishra-steps-down%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Navin%2C%20a%201993%20batch%20Indian%20Revenue%20Service%20officer%2C%20will%20hold%20the%20charge%20until%20a%20regular%20director%20is%20appointed%20or%20until%20further%20orders%2C%20a%20late-night%20notification%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Revenue%20said.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fed-special-director-rahul-navin-appointed-as-acting-chief-as-sanjay-mishra-steps-down%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Swiss%20NGO%20says%2018%20staff%20members%20detained%20in%20Afghanistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694844973000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103709373%2Cimgsize-42132.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fswiss-ngo-says-18-staff-members-detained-in-afghanistan%2Farticleshow%2F103708857.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103708857.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Taliban%20authorities%20in%20Afghanistan%20have%20detained%2018%20staff%20members%20of%20a%20Swiss-registered%20NGO%2C%20including%20a%20foreigner.%20The%20International%20Assistance%20Mission%20(IAM)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20operating%20in%20Afghanistan%20since%201966%2C%20said%20the%20staffers%20were%20taken%20from%20its%20office%20in%20Ghor%20province%20and%20brought%20to%20Kabul.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20staff%20members%20is%20currently%20unknown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fswiss-ngo-says-18-staff-members-detained-in-afghanistan%2Farticleshow%2F103708857.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fswiss-ngo-says-18-staff-members-detained-in-afghanistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F103708857.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fswiss-ngo-says-18-staff-members-detained-in-afghanistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F103708857.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98From%20My%20Grandma%E2%80%99s%20Kitchen%20to%20Yours%E2%80%99%3A%20Journalist%20Chronicles%20History%20of%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Heirloom%20Recipes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETanya%20Abraham%2C%20a%20journalist%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20Fort%20Kochi.%20Her%20childhood%20was%20largely%20shaped%20by%20two%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20food%20and%20history.%20The%20women%20in%20her%20home%2C%20particularly%20her%20grandmother%2C%20Annie%20Burleigh%20Kurishingal%2C%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20this.%20As%20did%20the%20city.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETanya%20grew%20up%20witnessing%20a%20confluence%20of%20cultures%20%E2%80%94%20Jews%2C%20Arabs%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20Konkani%20Brahmins.%20Through%20the%20years%2C%20their%20stories%20become%20windows%20through%20which%20she%20viewed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329731%2Fschool-friends-start-a-chutney-business-that-earns-in-lakhs-per-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculinary%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20history%20intrigued%20her%2C%20as%20did%20their%20food.%20And%20in%20a%20quest%20to%20dive%20deeper%20into%20these%20hidden%20treasures%2C%20she%20wrote%20%E2%80%98Fort%20Cochin%E2%80%99%20in%202009%2C%20followed%20ten%20years%20later%20by%20%E2%80%98Eating%20with%20History%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20she%20dedicated%20to%20her%20grandmother.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20recipes%20in%20this%20book%20%5BEating%20with%20History%5D%20have%20been%20soul%20food%20to%20someone%20at%20some%20point%20in%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%20For%20Tanya%2C%20her%20own%20fondest%20memories%20involve%20her%20%3Cem%3Eammama%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20book%2C%20she%20recalls%20how%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20starch%20white%20%3Cem%3Echatta%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%3Cem%3E%20mundu%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditional%20attire%20worn%20by%20catholic%20women%20in%20Kerala)%20yellowed%20through%20the%20day%20as%20%3Cem%3Emasalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20stained%20it.%20Long%20hours%20of%20working%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekushinchya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(kitchen)%20to%20serve%20a%20large%20joint%20family%20of%2030%20were%20to%20blame.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20was%20forgotten%20as%20the%20guests%20relished%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329667%2Fpalghar-kiran-kamdar-free-homemade-khichdi-for-patients-hospital-parkinson-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomemade%20rose%20cookies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20devoured%20the%20%3Cem%3Emeen%20pollichathu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fish%20cooked%20in%20banana%20leaves)%20dish.%20These%20frequent%20visitors%20were%20not%20always%20relatives%2C%20but%20a%20host%20of%20businessmen%2C%20political%20people%2C%20nationalists%2C%20and%20missionaries%2C%20all%20part%20of%20the%20Independence%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%2C%20she%20discovered%2C%20was%20always%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20home.%20And%20still%20is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20her%20%3Cem%3Eammama%3C%2Fem%3E%20passed%20away%20at%20the%20ripe%20old%20age%20of%20104%2C%20to%20Tanya%20it%20felt%20almost%20like%20a%20storehouse%20of%20culinary%20delights%20went%20away%20with%20her.%20It%20made%20her%20think%20of%20all%20the%20women%20who%2C%20like%20her%20grandmother%2C%20had%20brewed%20magic%20through%20their%20recipes.%20These%20would%20be%20lost%20in%20time%20if%20not%20preserved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuelled%20by%20this%20thought%2C%20Tanya%20went%20on%20%E2%80%9Ca%20life-changing%20journey%E2%80%9D%20across%20Kerala%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C