hnologies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20thankfully%2C%20I%20already%20had%20bought%2015-acre%20land%20to%20practise%20farming.%20So%20for%20those%20two%20years%2C%20I%20continued%20to%20earn%20by%20growing%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20like%20oranges%2C%20soybean%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Etuar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pigeon%20pea)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20he%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20a%20bank%20and%20restarted%20the%20business%20with%2020%2C000%20egg-laying%20hens.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20profits%2C%20I%20kept%20on%20increasing%20the%20birds%20at%20my%20farm.%20Today%2C%20I%20have%201.8%20lakh%20hens%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravindra%2C%20who%20has%20been%20doing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54545%2Fwomen-farmers-empowerment-fighting-maharashtra-drought%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoultry%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20he%20now%20earns%20up%20to%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20day%20through%20this%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESharing%20learnings%20with%20new%20IAS%20officers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies%20like%20indoor%20vertical%20farming%2C%20greenhouse%20farming%2C%20automatic%20watering%2C%20drip%20systems%2C%20remote%20sensing%20irrigation%20systems%2C%20and%20organic%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20employed%20only%2050%20workers%20to%20manage%20my%20poultry%20farm%20spread%20across%2050%20acres.%20Most%20of%20the%20work%20is%20automated.%20For%20example%2C%20from%20collecting%20eggs%20from%20broilers%20and%20giving%20feed%20to%20poultry%20birds%2C%20to%20collecting%20their%20excreta%2C%20everything%20is%20ensured%20using%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%202013