nna%20in%20this%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shreyas%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tangy%20and%20spicy%20journey%20towards%20delicious%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20started%20to%20work%20on%20their%20idea%20two%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20set%20up%20a%20research%20and%20development%20centre%20in%20Ambattur%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20had%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%2C%20technologists%20and%20culinary%20experts%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20simplify%20chutney-making%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prasanna%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20things%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20tackle%20with%20chutneys%20were%20to%20shorten%20the%20time%20of%20preparation%20as%20it%20takes%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20chopping%2C%20mixing%20and%20blending.%20Secondly%2C%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20address%20the%20quantity%20issues.%20In%20households%2C%20chutney%20is%20never%20made%20for%20one%20person.%20But%20we%20prepared%20our%20chutney%20in%20smaller%20batches%20that%20can%20be%20consumed%20by%20one%20person%20too.%20Lastly%2C%20we%20noticed%20how%20supermarkets%20did%20not%20sell%20traditional%20chutneys%20and%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20bring%20them%20back%20into%20the%20mainstream%20food%20palette%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20their%20products%2C%20there%20are%20only%20three%20steps%20involved%20in%20making%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20you%20crack%20open%20the%20seal%2C%20second%2C%20pour%20water%20as%20per%20your%20requirement%2C%20and%20third%2C%20enjoy%20it%20from%20the%20cup%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20are%20serving%2014%20varieties%20of%20chutneys%20and%20have%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fyati-5-1694527695-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329745%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20are%20serving%2014%20varieties%20of%20chutneys%20and%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chutnefy%20Team%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20fathers%2C%20the%20duo%20wanted%20to%20ease%20the%20pressure%20of%20strenuous%20cooking%20off%20of%20their%20wives%2C%20so%20they%20created%20a%20brand%20which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20time%20consuming.%20The%20brand%20wants%20to%20cater%20to%20not%20just%20the%20busy%20moms%20but%20also%20to%20those%20bachelors%20who%20come%20home%20after%20a%20long%20day%20at%20work%20and%20want%20to%20eat%20something%20yummy%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20include%20takeout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20pre-cooked%20food%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20laden%20with%20additives%20and%20preservatives.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20something%20that%20was%20authentic%20and%20preservative-free.%20Our%20products%20have%20a%20comparatively%20shorter%20shelf-life%20of%20just