k%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%20In%20Dungarpur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20she%20helped%20farmers%20move%20from%20farming%20just%20one%20crop%20%E2%80%94%20corn%20%E2%80%94%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20crops%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCrops%20like%20maize%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20water.%20So%20we%20helped%20the%20tribal%20farmers%20in%20Dungarpurby%20showing%20them%20how%20to%20cultivate%20crops%20like%20%3Cem%3Emoong%20%3C%2Fem%3E(green%20gram)%20using%20less%20water%20on%20their%20farms%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20partnership%20with%20ITC%E2%80%99s%20e-Choupal.%20This%20way%2C%20the%20farmers%20always%20have%20a%20backup%20crop%20in%20case%20one%20fails.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20also%20gained%20access%20to%20ITC%E2%80%99s%20marketplace.%20We%20also%20assisted%20farmers%20in%20growing%20millets%2C%20which%20require%20less%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDipti%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Dungarpur%2C%20says%20they%20have%20benefited%20from%20this%20programme%2C%20and%20that%20today%2C%20they%20also%20grow%20vegetables.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20my%20husband%20would%20have%20to%20go%20to%20other%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20work%20if%20our%20crop%20failed.%20Now%2C%20as%20we%20are%20growing%20lentils%20and%20vegetables%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20sustain%20ourselves%20well.%20We%20are%20able%20to%20manage%20even%20with%20less%20water%2C%20as%20we%20have%20a%20multitude%20of%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnleashing%20the%20magic%20of%20millet%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20540px)%20100vw%2C%20540px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe